name: evolutionary fragment
description: Generation 600. Samples drawn from a partially trained Wasserstein-GP GAN, at an evolutionary stage where the basic form has started to segment and colour and the pattern from the CNN deconvolution upsampling mixes with the emerging dominant shades. Edition of 22, 10% royalty. An offshoot of Sempervivum Rickshaw with Jane Le Besque. Created and minted 25.06.21.
